#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:1
msgid "Cross-compiling for Mobile devices"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:4
msgid ""
"For complete build instructions see [here](../build_instructions/build.md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:7
msgid ""
"VTK supports mobile devices in its build. These are triggered by a top-level "
"flag which then exposes some settings for a cross-compiled VTK that is "
"controlled from the top-level build."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:11
msgid "IOS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:13
msgid ""
"iOS builds may be enabled by setting the `VTK_IOS_BUILD` option. The "
"following settings than affect the iOS build:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:16
msgid "`IOS_SIMULATOR_ARCHITECTURES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:17
msgid "`IOS_DEVICE_ARCHITECTURES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:18
msgid "`IOS_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:19
msgid "`IOS_EMBED_BITCODE`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:21
msgid "Android"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:23
msgid ""
"Android builds may be enabled by setting the `VTK_ANDROID_BUILD` option. "
"Android build use a set of defined option in `vtkAndroid.cmake` but user "
"options can also be added by setting `VTK_ANDROID_USER_OPTIONS`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:27
msgid "The following settings affect the Android build:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:29
msgid "`ANDROID_NDK`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:30
msgid "`ANDROID_NATIVE_API_LEVEL`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:31
msgid "`ANDROID_ARCH_ABI`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/build_for_mobile.md:33
msgid ""
"A typical CMake configuration line would be: `cmake -S /vtk-src -B /vtk-"
"build  -DANDROID_ARCH_ABI=arm64-v8a -DANDROID_NATIVE_API_LEVEL=34 -"
"DANDROID_NDK=/path/to/ndk -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DVTK_ANDROID_BUILD=ON -"
"DVTK_ANDROID_USER_OPTIONS=\"-DVTK_MODULE_ENABLE_VTK_IOInfovis=NO;-"
"DVTK_MODULE_ENABLE_VTK_TestingRendering=NO\"`"
msgstr ""
